column2: select top # P.objid, P.ra as sdss_ra, P.dec as sdss_dec, W.ra as wise_ra, W.dec as wise_dec, S.specobjid, S.class, S.z as redshift, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, P.dered_u, P.dered_g, P.dered_r, P.dered_i, P.dered_z, P.err_u, P.err_g, P.err_r, P.err_i, P.err_z, W.w1mpro, W.w2mpro, W.w3mpro, W.w4mpro, W.w1sigmpro, W.w2sigmpro, W.w3sigmpro, W.w4sigmpro from dbo.WISE_xmatch as X join dbo.WISE_allsky as W on X.wise_cntr = W.cntr join dbo.PhotoObjAll as P on X.sdss_objid = P.objid join dbo.SpecObjAll as S on objid = P.objid where W.w1mpro > #*W.w1sigmpro and W.w2mpro > #*W.w2sigmpro and W.w3mpro > #*W.w3sigmpro
